{
  "stem": "26609.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went once-- once, twice in a month, we had to go over there, and to listen to lectures, and see around how it is, you know, with patients, everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But otherwise, no contact, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, but, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't come in contact with other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were mostly-- we lived near [INAUDIBLE] hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'll tell you about this hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was known.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that hospital, there were only Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was always full of patients, because there were always a lot of sick people then, more than-- maybe more than today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The hospital was always full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of my uncles-- my father's sister, a younger sister, only sister-- from Grodek, he was her husband.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was brought there to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know what he'd suffered from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he was sick and had to be at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they brought him from Grodek to this hospital, and he was there quite for a long time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it happened that that was just before the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ghetto was already there, established.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, he wouldn't go to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During the German occupation, people were not-- Jewish people were not admitted to hospitals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish-- even the Jewish one was closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was from before there, and it was full of his other patients.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Germans-- it was end of '92.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think the-- the ghetto was closed already in-- in beginning of '93, if I remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was still at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know what they did?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They locked the hospital all around and burned it alive with all the patients.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was known in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if anyone told the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
